Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.66,Superscript,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Man, that was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:23.00,Title,,0,0,0,,A Guy You Like, or a Guy from the Past?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:20.46,Superscript,Otani,0,0,0,,It freaking rocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:21.47,Superscript,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I was so worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.80,Superscript,Otani,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:26.34,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,But as expected, that song was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.87,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It was awesome hearing it live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.21,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:29.91,Overlap,Otani,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:30.87,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'm still totally worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.87,0:01:31.91,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It was just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:32.51,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.55,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:39.82,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:41.62,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.46,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Who are you?! Who are you?! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.63,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,It's me, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:49.59,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Fukagawa Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.16,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:53.93,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:57.33,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I lived near you when we were in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:58.94,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:18.72,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Risa is recollecting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:18.72,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Recall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.61,Default,boyone,0,0,0,,He's a boy but his name is Haruka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:09.01,Default,boytwo,0,0,0,,He must have boobies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.32,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I don't have boobies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:12.48,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.62,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You guys are teasing Haruka again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.05,Default,boyone,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.06,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.66,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Oh... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.56,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You're that Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.89,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm that Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.90,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Wow! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.60,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I hardly recognized you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.77,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I thought you went overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.03,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.39,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You've grown taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.74,Overlap,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm 185cm now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:33.64,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:35.64,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm taller than you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:37.47,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.98,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Boy, this brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:40.88,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I've got to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:41.91,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.85,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Wait... Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:45.72,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,It sure does bring back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.05,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,How's your mom doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.39,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Good. How's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.72,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,My family? Everyone's doing pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.49,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Which school are you going to now, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Maido High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.50,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.55,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Everyone! Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.98,Default,group,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.85,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Yo! I haven't seen you for a while. \NYou're getting even taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.72,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.00,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,How are things going with your ex-girlfriend these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.00,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.81,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,How about you, Koizumi? \NWho was that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.81,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.91,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,The guy that suddenly hugged you in the middle of the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.65,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.65,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,He's a childhood friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.12,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,He moved overseas when we were in the fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:00.99,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Do you actually care?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.73,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You're the one who's always saying "ex this," and "ex that."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.55,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Please bless me with a boyfriend this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.59,Overlap,Otani,0,0,0,,Hey, something's coming out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.77,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.83,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,This way. Come on, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.83,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.33,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Go on, go on, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.23,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.27,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Kanzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.37,Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.71,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Uh... H-How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.34,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.32,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Is this the girl you went to the Christmas concert with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.15,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'm Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.95,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Sorry to cause all that trouble a few days back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:05.96,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I didn't realize that Atsushi-kun was seeing someone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.02,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.96,Default,group,0,0,0,,No, no, no! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.73,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,There's absolutely nothing going on between me and Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.90,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,There's no love between us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.27,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,So if there's something you want to tell Otani,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.34,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,...don't hesitate for my sake and say whatever you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.04,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Okay?! Okay?! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.14,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'll do everything I can to support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.84,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what happened between you two, but I'll support—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.95,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What the hell did you say just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.05,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.42,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,This is important to you, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.59,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Just hear her out, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.92,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.16,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:39.89,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.56,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,I didn't choose him because of his height!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.63,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:48.00,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,It's just that the person I liked happened to be tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.74,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,I don't dislike Atsushi-kun because he's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:52.74,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:57.64,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Later when I thought about it, I realized it looked like I'd done something awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.08,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,But even so, I felt really awkward about explaining it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.31,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Um... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.88,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.82,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,...was that what you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:08.75,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.62,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,It was good to get it off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.89,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,I feel much better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:15.93,Default,Kanzaki,0,0,0,,Bye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.74,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,So... Sorry, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.27,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! Truly sorry! Extremely sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:29.67,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.74,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.01,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You can hit me, kick me, do whatever you want to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:34.81,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.08,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.52,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I had no idea that was what she wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.95,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I though she wanted to get back together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.19,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,It was really none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.32,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.82,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I heard what she had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.09,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.00,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You should be more upset! What I did was—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.73,Overlap,Otani,0,0,0,,That's enough, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:54.73,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:58.30,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I was holding onto a bit of hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.24,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,...but I've completely given up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:07.11,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I'm just saying that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.71,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What... do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.82,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Oh, there! There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.25,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Hey, want to go get some lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.76,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:26.86,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,In the end, the boyfriend/girlfriend challenge didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.47,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,When I finally realized that, it was already Valentines Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.57,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.37,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,...chocolate cake or chocolate cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.11,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Which is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:39.14,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Cookies are much easier to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.21,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.61,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Say, why don't we make those cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.38,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Okay. They look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.08,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You guys seem pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.05,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,I asked you to join us, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:53.09,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I have no one to give cookies to, even if I do make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.62,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,You have Otani, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.33,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.56,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Why should I give cookies to Otani?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.33,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,He ended up with his feelings hurt again because of your mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.57,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,...so you owe him a pretty big apology, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.37,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.14,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Right? It's a good idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.44,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:14.98,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What's up? You look pretty happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.31,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Lend me your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.35,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,My ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.01,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.42,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.12,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,New song by Umibouzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.75,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.09,Superscript,,0,0,0,,U M I B O U Z U
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.46,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's their album from when they were with an indie label.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.46,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I found it at a second-hand music store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.26,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.70,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,This is a discontinued release, so it's hard to find now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.43,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.80,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,They get along well, don't they.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.63,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,They're both so carried away that they could totally get together right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.17,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Is Umibouzu responsible for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.32,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I made this chocolate myself. \NPlease accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:58.46,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Hey, do you want chocolate cake or cookies for Valentines Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.02,Default,nakao,0,0,0,,What? Are you going to make something yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.09,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Yeah. Risa's going to be helping us out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh? You're talking about that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.53,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh? How sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.03,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Who'd fall victim to such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.37,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What do you mean "fall victim to"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:12.44,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,If any guy eats chocolate made by this amazon, he'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.44,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,And he'll probably grow huge to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:16.81,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:17.87,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.88,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,No one would be happy to receive chocolate made by a huge girl like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:24.98,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I've never even been on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.98,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I don't have any fans who think I'm cute, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.25,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:32.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I... I....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:32.92,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:37.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I'll probably never give out any chocolate until the day I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.16,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Calm down, Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.20,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What's up with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.87,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Why are you always acting so strangely?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.13,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.44,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.37,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You can give me your chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.58,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I don't want you to accept it half-heartedly out of pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:54.61,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.31,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I like sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.62,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's okay if you'd rather not give it to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.32,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Oh... I like chocolate cake, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.09,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I-I-I never said I'd make anything for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.93,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.57,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Otani, you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.20,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.31,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:25.74,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:29.85,Default,Random,0,0,0,,We always see you and Otani-kun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.15,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Are you guys going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.02,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh? No, no. It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.22,Default,Random,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.95,Default,Random,0,0,0,,That would be impossible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.56,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Otani-kun wouldn't date a huge girl like that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.06,Default,Random,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.70,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Those girls will be giving Otani chocolate too, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.40,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:53.24,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,If he's going to receive so much chocolate, he probably won't need mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.00,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.47,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.54,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa! It's so nice to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.25,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Ughh... Haruka, I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.05,Default,nakao,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.89,Default,nakao,0,0,0,,Phew. That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.46,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.50,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Why'd that guy come to our school yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.51,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,He came to complete his student-transfer paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.94,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh? He's transferring here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.94,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's starting in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.51,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Oh, That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.15,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,He's your type, right Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:41.62,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Ah, no way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.45,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,He used to be a hopeless crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.86,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Haruka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:50.23,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,His grandma's British, so he used to look just like a foreign girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.30,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,All his friends were girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.43,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,...and he had a girly personality, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:56.20,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What a hopeless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.03,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Too true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.64,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,He may be good looking now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.01,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:06.08,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I should have said he was my ex-boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.35,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,How stupid am I?! I'm too honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.81,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.02,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I thought I was about to lose to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:16.75,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,...but I guess it's not that easy for a tall girl to get a boyfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.12,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:20.12,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Anyway, you don't have any plans today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.03,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Let's go to the CD store and look for some more Umibouzu CD's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.19,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.20,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:30.40,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Risa, this chocolate cake looks really easy to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.23,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Let's make this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.47,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Oh, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:34.80,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Chocolate cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.71,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I'd better have my stomach pills ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.58,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,S-screw you! I'm not making it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.88,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Not for you, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.11,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.26,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.36,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,He's here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.36,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.03,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.56,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,If you're free, let's have tea together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:05.54,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry. I've already made plans with Otani today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.67,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.74,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay. I—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.27,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,What...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:12.01,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,What on earth is this little creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.38,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.98,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, Risa,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.18,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,...you were taking this little guy out for a walk a few days ago too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.28,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't talk about me like I'm a pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:22.42,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're not fit to be seen with a beauty like Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.79,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.89,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,How is she a beauty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.76,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.79,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Gee, I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.76,Overlap,Otani,0,0,0,,This guy's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.43,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,There must be something wrong with his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.86,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,What's your problem?! \NYou're so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:35.93,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Who are you calling rude?! \NWanna fight, baldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.07,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,How am I bald? Are you an Idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:40.44,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:43.31,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,This guy keeps getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.17,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Now, now. Take it easy, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.31,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.81,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Is this the guy you just told me you had plans with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:49.61,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.05,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.22,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're so cool, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.42,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,It's totally uncool for you to be seen with a midget like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.76,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You've been my hero for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.26,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I hope that you'll always be as cool as you were back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.26,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Your hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.36,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.26,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Even if I kill you, God will forgive me for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.50,Default,nakao,0,0,0,,Calm down, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.50,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Shut up, midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.50,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa is my personal hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.74,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I won't let you have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.61,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.24,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Let's go, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.57,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.11,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:24.95,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't say something so unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,Day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.89,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Uh... About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.59,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka isn't really a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:38.90,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever come across such a mean guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.30,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.53,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't get me involved in such an unreasonable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.93,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.37,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka said that stuff out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.30,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You're the hero. Do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:48.60,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,The hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:49.97,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,The hero, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.48,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,A man who needs a woman's protection is just pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.18,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:57.15,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,It's even more pathetic for a man to be that short.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.21,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.55,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.38,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Good morning, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.09,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I made you a lunch box.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.09,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Do you like wieners?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.16,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't go barging into other people's classrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.73,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You're not a student here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.96,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.10,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're quite a noisy midget, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:17.13,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,A midget should act like a midget. Now be quiet and stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:19.37,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.54,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,...could you go over there for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:28.85,Sign,,0,0,0,,Idiot Trio
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.58,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Look, we've captured an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.38,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Arghh! I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:34.45,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks for the lunch box. You'd better get going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.15,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Huh? So soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.45,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Hey. Otani, who was that guy just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.39,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Her childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.46,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Those two look pretty good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.79,Default,Random,0,0,0,,They're both tall like models.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.46,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Koizumi-san is really pretty, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.30,Default,Random,0,0,0,,I've always thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.40,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right. She's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:55.54,Default,Random,0,0,0,,But she looks like one half of All Hanshin-Kyoujin when she's with Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.41,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You guys are gonna say the same thing he did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.41,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,What the hell?! Is it my fault that Koizumi's so freaking tall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.31,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:03.05,Default,Random,0,0,0,,It does kinda seem that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.62,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,So tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.75,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Amazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:08.18,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.12,Default,Random,0,0,0,,All Hanshin-Kyojin returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.23,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,Your cake looks really nice, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.63,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Do I seriously have to give this to Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.07,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.60,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Never mind. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:29.41,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Otani is already super mad at me because of Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.28,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,I wonder if Haruka-kun likes you, Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:36.65,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,"Like"? That guy only sees me as his hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:37.75,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,His hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.18,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,A hero is normally a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.99,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,I don't look very feminine, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.59,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,But he said you were beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.02,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.52,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,If you were more serious about it, you'd probably be really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.62,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.26,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to be more serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.93,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Take part in girly activities from time to time, like a girl, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.16,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.94,Default,Tanaka,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.90,Default,Ishihara,0,0,0,,Something is coming out of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:09.85,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:11.78,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.42,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.52,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,How come you say you don't want it now? \NYou're making me feel stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:17.29,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You don't care?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Valentines Day doesn't mean anything to me, but you said you wanted this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.76,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Who said they wanted it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:28.16,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,I only said if you had nobody to give your chocolate to, you could give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.00,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,That's why I am giving this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.40,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,You have that annoying Haruka now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.61,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.34,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Oh, Koizumi is giving chocolate to Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.98,Default,Random,0,0,0,,No way! Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:44.31,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Y-You've got it all wrong! I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.85,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's a CD! It's a CD I wanted to borrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.98,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.99,Default,Random,0,0,0,,Liar. I can smell chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.92,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.62,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,It's for her childhood friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.19,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.06,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:04.00,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Fine then. I'm giving this to Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.82,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.03,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.70,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.03,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I came to pick you up again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.80,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,That's an excuse, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.90,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I was actually hoping to receive Valentine's chocolates from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.74,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.05,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Really?! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.21,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,It's nothing. You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.05,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'll never eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.79,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it my entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.92,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Don't keep it! You'd better eat it quickly, otherwise it'll go bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.42,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,But I kept the chocolates you gave me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.02,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Don't keep them! Just throw them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.06,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.20,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Want to hang out with me for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.47,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:16.91,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Heh, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.28,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Ahh, I feel much better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.61,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're still so good when it comes to games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.98,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're cool no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:31.49,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Hearing that doesn't make me happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.59,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Why? That's what I like most about you, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.19,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're the only one who would say a thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:42.16,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Everyone's always calling me All Hanshin-Kyojin at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.27,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,That's because you've always got that midget hanging around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:46.24,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,What's your relationship with that guy, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.91,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Our relationship? \NIt's not like we have a relationship, as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.78,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,We're just in the same class, and walk home the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.24,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're cool, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.45,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time hanging around with him. He's totally uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.35,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,You say that, but he actually has a lot of good qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:04.35,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,He trains really hard at basketball, even though he's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:09.66,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,And whenever I'm in trouble, he always come to my rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.96,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,And on Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.34,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.94,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, he's not a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.64,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.01,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,...you like that guy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:31.75,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:33.48,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.15,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.02,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.96,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I won't lose to that midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:43.13,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.70,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,I always dreamed that you'd one day be my girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.27,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,...and we'd spend our high school days together, swept up in romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:54.67,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,One of these days I'll declare my love for you, and ask you to be my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.11,Default,Haruka,0,0,0,,Please think about how you'll answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.80,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.34,Default,Koizumi,0,0,0,,Never mind. It was only obligatory chocolate, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.04,Default,Otani,0,0,0,,Right. Obligatory chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:46.36,Superscript,,0,0,0,,OBLIGATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani is kissing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The era of short guys is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Kiss! I've Fallen for You!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
